    "title": "京东开放平台不当获取/使用信息违规细则",
    "followRuleId": "3396",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【违规定义】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不当获取/使用信息：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指通过包括但不限于租借/共享账号、协助第三方扫描系统等方式获取平台商业信息/他人信息，或未经允许发布、传递、出售平台商业信息/他人信息，致使平台商业信息/他人信息存在泄露风险或已发生泄露，或商家违反信息安全相关法律法规、协议或规则的行为，包括但不限于盗用他人京东账户，涉嫌侵犯他人相关信息、财产权的行为。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">京东有权视违规程度对商家及其关联店铺进行预警及开具违约单，采取扣除违约金、减少店铺曝光（包括但不限于对全店商品操作降权/屏蔽、禁止投放广告、禁止提报营销活动等）、商品下架且禁止上架、降低店铺星级、限制使用特定的权益工具或管理工具（包括但不限于限制使用第三方平台快递单号出库、限制使用ISV工具等）、冻结钱包、店铺账号封禁、执行店铺清退。</span> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则解读】</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、不当获取/使用信息里的&ldquo;信息&rdquo;指什么？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">不当获取/使用信息里的&ldquo;信息&rdquo;指&ldquo;平台商业信息&rdquo;和&ldquo;他人信息&rdquo;。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台商业信息是指平台的产品、技术、软件、程序、数据等信息，包含但不限于店铺信息、创作者信息、团长信息、商品信息、成交额、搜索、浏览、加购、订单、评价等相关信息。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">他人信息包括但不限于：真实姓名、手机号码、收货地址、身份证信息、及其他涉及他人隐私权或人身权或商业秘密等相关信息。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、商家不当获取/使用信息的情形有哪些？</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家不当获取/使用信息的情形包括但不限于商家在未经平台或他人事先许可的情况下，进行如下任一行为：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、向第三方租借账号；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、与第三方共享账号；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、自行、授权或协助第三方对平台商业信息或平台系统进行地址扫描、网络端口扫描、操作系统探测等扫描或探测；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、自行、授权或协助第三方以包括通过机器人、蜘蛛等程序或设备监视、复制、传播、展示、镜像、上传、下载等方式擅自获取使用平台商业信息；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、向第三方有偿或无偿提供平台商业信息或他人信息；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、对外披露、共享平台商业信息或他人信息；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家违规使用第三方软件，导致平台商业信息或他人信息存在泄露风险或已经发生泄露；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家在职员工或员工离职前，滥用/泄露平台商业信息或他人信息；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、商家违规开通子账号，滥用/泄露平台商业信息或他人信息 ；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、盗用他人账户；</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、其他未经允许或违反有关信息数据安全的法律法规、政策文件、协议、规则等。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">三、<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">违规严重程度档位说明</span> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 32px; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">平台根据违规行为对用户体验造成的伤害程度，从轻到重执行M1到M7档位违约金，具体金额如下：</span></p>\n<table style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 100%; word-break: break-all; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 48.2pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">档位</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 99.2pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">用户体验伤害分级</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 367.7pt; background-color: #dc1623;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">违约金标准</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 48.2pt;\" width=\"64\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">M1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 99.2pt;\" width=\"132\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 28px; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">体验伤害一级</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0.75pt; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 367.7pt;\" width=\"490\">\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size